"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.1.7\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.1.7</span> 標題：捆、禾捆（sheaf）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： אֲלֻמָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ’alumah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:7\">GEN 37:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:7\">GEN 37:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:7\">GEN 37:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:7\">GEN 37:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps126:6\">PSA 126:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： עָמִיר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ‘amir)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:21\">JER 9:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:13\">AMO 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:12\">MIC 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:6\">ZEC 12:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： עמר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ‘imer（動詞）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps129:7\">PSA 129:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： עֹמֶר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ‘omer)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:12\">LEV 23:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:15\">LEV 23:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:19\">DEU 24:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:7\">RUT 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:15\">RUT 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:10\">JOB 24:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： δράγμα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： dragma)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt8:3\">JDT 8:3</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0934_sheaf.jpg\" alt=\"收穫的穀穗\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">收穫的穀穗 ( Jakub Hałun © Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>禾捆是將收割下來的農作物的稈和穗子捆在一起而形成的束，通常就用農作物的稈來捆扎。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>收割穀物時，可以用鐮刀貼近地面將其割下來（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.1.6 鐮刀 (sickle)&lt;REALIA:1.1.6&gt;</a> ），或者用手拔出來。然後，把許多穀物的稈攏成束，在中間將其捆扎起來，成為一捆。如果這些禾捆不是立即搬走，那麼可以豎立在地上，以免穗子接觸潮濕的地面。把禾捆聚攏到一起後，就可以送去禾場（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.1.8.1 禾場 (threshing floor)&lt;REALIA:1.1.8.1&gt;</a> ）。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在翻譯「禾捆」一詞時，翻譯者可以使用描述性的短語，例如「一束收穫的穀物」。在有些文化中，人們並不知道將穀物捆成捆的做法。有些語言可能必須採用「捆在一起的穀物」這類短語來表達。有些經文需要具體指明是哪種穀物。有時，翻譯者需要將「禾捆」寬泛地翻譯成「莊稼」（“harvest”，如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 的<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps126:6\">PSA 126:6</a> ；比較<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:10\">JOB 24:10</a> 中的譯詞，“wheat”「小麥」），甚至譯成「穀物」（“grain”，如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 的<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:13\">AMO 2:13</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:12\">MIC 4:12</a> ）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 在比較寬泛的意義上翻譯「禾捆」的另一處經文是<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt8:3\">JDT 8:3</a> 。這節經文的原文直譯為：「當他站在那裡，監督那些在田間捆禾捆的人的時候」，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 採用了直譯，但<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 英文直譯作「在地裡監督農民的時候」。</p>\n<p>實際上，希伯來文<em>‘amir</em> 和<em>‘omer</em> 是指放在田邊的許多禾捆形成的堆，還沒有被送到禾場，因此<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:13\">AMO 2:13</a> 的重點是在穀物的總重量。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
